    regolith-styles,
    regolith-unclutter-xfixes,
    rofi,
    xrescat
Suggests:
    update-manager,
    software-properties-gtk
Multi-Arch: foreign
Description: metapackage for Regolith desktop environment
 This package contains all the packages necessary for the 
 desktop environment to function.

